      "title": "A dead body of a youth was recovered from Kilinochchi Ambalkulam",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The body of a youth has been recovered from Ambalkulam in Kilinochchi this afternoon, according to the Kilinochchi Police.",
        "A 19-year-old man named Raghu from Mankulam area has been living in Pourpupulam area.",
        "The body will be taken to the Kilinochchi Hospital for an autopsy after a complaint was lodged at the Kilinochchi Police Station."
      ],
